NCL Text Editor README
=====================
This is NCL Text Editor, an advanced text editor for NCL Language.

NCL Text Editor is based on QScintilla as the main API to colourize,
autocomplete and other advanced features.

To see how to update the QScintilla code go to deps/HOW_TO_UPDATE_QSCINTILLA.

