Supported platforms
-------------------
Currently we have support for:
- Windows
- Linux
- MacOSX 10.6

The specific platforms that have been used for testing are:
- Windows: Windows Vista.
- MacOSX 10.6: Recent Core.
- Linux: Ubuntu 10.10.

